title: Electromax Water Boiling Jug 2L
description:
• About products:-

  • This 2L cordless electric kettle boils water 85% more efficiently than a stovetop kettle.
  • Concealed stainless steel heating element; automatic shut-off after the boil, with dry protection
  • Durable stainless steel body.
  • Non-slip 360-degrees rotary power base for cordless easy filling, pouring, and serving with 50cm chord stored neatly in the base
  • One can boil milk and make tea in the kettle too.
